    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">An ASR Outdoor camping gear essential! Whether you’re installing a canopy, tent, or overhead covering for a camping trip, sporting event, or other, these aluminum tent stakes can take on all of it! The ASR Outdoor lightweight aluminum camping gear tent stakes feature single-body construction from top to bottom and are forged from aircraft-grade 6061 aluminum; Known for their strength, work-ability, and resistance to corrosion, these tent pegs will see you through many camping seasons to come! And, with the handy stringing eyelet at the head and sharp tip at the foot of the tent stake, the installation will be a breeze. Plus, their vibrant orange color makes the tent stakes easy to spot for adjustments or removal, even in dim or dusk lighting</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor 9 Inch Aircraft Grade Aluminum Camping Stakes Tent Pegs (Pack Sizes)</h2>\n  <p>An ASR Outdoor camping gear essential! Whether you’re installing a canopy, tent, or overhead covering for a camping trip, sporting event, or other, these aluminum tent stakes can take on all of it!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>CAMPING GEAR ESSENTIAL:</strong> Whether installing a tent, grow tent, canopy, camping tent, beach tent, pop up tent, tarp tent, pergola or overhead covering for a camping trip, sporting event or other, these aluminum tent stakes can handle all of it! And, with the handy stringing eyelet at the head and sharp tip at the foot of the tent stake, installation will be a breeze</li>\n    <li><strong>AIRCRAFT GRADE ALUMINUM:</strong> These heavy-duty, durable aluminum camping tent pegs are forged from aircraft grade 6061 aluminum; Known for its strength, workability and resistance to corrosion, the ASR Outdoor tent stakes will see you through many camping seasons to come</li>\n    <li><strong>SINGLE BODY CONSTRUCTION:</strong> The ASR Outdoor lightweight aluminum camping gear tent stakes feature single-body construction from top to bottom; this increases the tent pegs integrity, durability and longevity and makes installation and removal more efficient</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Dimensions: 9 Inch (l); Color: Red; Material: 6061 Aircraft Grade Aluminum</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/sports_outdoors/camping_hiking/915ATP_9in_aluminum_tent_peg_4_pk.jpg\" alt=\"An ASR Outdoor camping gear essential\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> RDTS4PCAL</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810058484338</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Red</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>The ASR Outdoor lightweight aluminum camping gear tent stakes feature single-body construction from top to bottom and are forged from aircraft-grade 6061 aluminum; Known for their strength, work-ability, and resistance to corrosion, these tent pegs will see you through many camping seasons to come! And, with the handy stringing eyelet at the head and sharp tip at the foot of the tent stake, the installation will be a breeze. Plus, their vibrant orange color makes the tent stakes easy to spot for adjustments or removal, even in dim or dusk lighting.</p>\n  <p>Length Dimensions: 9 inches; Assorted pack sizes available.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
